headline: 20 Years on Wall Street Taught Me: Boomers Feel Safe With 5 High-Yield Dividend Giants
summary: After a 35-year career in the finance industry, including two decades as an institutional stockbroker at Bear Stearns, Lehman Brothers, and Morgan Stanley, I developed an institutional perspective on dividend-focused investing.
